title: Blunt Talk S01E07 720p
description:
===================================================================================
British newscaster Walter Blunt comes to Los Angeles| intent on conquering the world of American cable TV. Through the platform of a nightly interview show| Blunt is
on a mission to impart his wisdom and guidance on how Americans should live| think and behave. Unfortunately| Blunt is constantly harassed by interfering network
bosses| a dysfunctional news staff| and his numerous ex-wives and children. Blunt must now deal with the fallout from his well-intended but misguided actions| both
on and off the air| with only an alcoholic manservant at his side.
===================================================================================
